{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"jQuery","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Glossary/jQuery","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>jQuery es una&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a> <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\">Library</a>&nbsp;que se enfoca en simplificar la manipulación del&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/DOM\">DOM</a>, llamadas&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/AJAX\">AJAX</a> y manejo de&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/event\">Event</a>. Es utilizado por desarrolladores JavaScript de manera frecuente.</p>\n\n<p>jQUery usa un formato,&nbsp;<code>$(selector).action()</code>&nbsp;para asignar elementos a un evento. Para explicarlo con mayor detalle, <code>$(selector)</code>&nbsp;hara que jQuery seleccione los elementos&nbsp;<code>selector</code>&nbsp;y los asigne a un evento&nbsp;<a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/API\">API</a> llamado&nbsp;<code>.action()</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">ready</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"¡Hola Mundo!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"#blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">hide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>El código anterior es equivalente al siguiente:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"¡Hola Mundo!\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"blackBox\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>style<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"none\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"descargar_jquery","title":"Descargar&nbsp;jQuery","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\"><strong>npm</strong></th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">bower (solo file)</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Google CDN</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>npm install jquery</code></td>\n   <td><code>bower install&nbsp;https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.min.js</code></td>\n   <td><code>https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js</code></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>","titleAsText":"Descargar jQuery"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"aprende_más","title":"Aprende más","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conocimiento_general","title":"Conocimiento general","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a title=\"jQuery\" href=\"https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/JQuery\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">jQuery</a> en Wikipedia</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Sitio oficial de jQuery</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"aprende_jquery","title":"Aprende jQuery","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.codecademy.com/learn/jquery\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Curso web en codeacademy.com</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"información_técnica","title":"Información técnica","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Documentación de referencia de la API</a><a href=\"https://api.jquery.com/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\"> </a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Descargar&nbsp;jQuery","id":"descargar_jquery"},{"text":"Aprende más","id":"aprende_más"}],"summary":"jQuery es una JavaScript Library que se enfoca en simplificar la manipulación del DOM, llamadas AJAX y manejo de Event. Es utilizado por desarrolladores JavaScript de manera frecuente.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"jQuery","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"jQuery","locale":"ru","native":